0.4a - 0.5a

	- SSLEX now uses a parser generated by SSLR V0.5a
	- SSLEX warns about reg. exp. of the kind {FOO}*, as these are only
	  useful when another reg. exp. is following

0.3a - 0.4a

	- corrected manual

0.2a - 0.3a

	- several bugfixes
	- SSLEX now uses a scanner generated by SSLEX itself
	- valgrinded sslex

0.1a - 0.2a

	- bugfixes
	- improved the dea-state-minimizing routine
	- improvements in the generated scanner

